# Recover — environment variables
#
# Optional. Leave UNSET to run in built-in MOCK mode (realistic canned
# reasoning, zero setup). Set this to your Anthropic API key to switch the
# agent's reasoning to LIVE claude-sonnet-4-6 calls.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the value:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# NOTE: Vite exposes any var prefixed with VITE_ to the browser bundle. This
# MVP calls the Anthropic API directly from the browser for demo simplicity,
# so the key ships to the client. Fine for a local/demo throwaway key — do NOT
# use a production key here. See README for the production-safe pattern.
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
